OL,3,CSir Bobby Charlton's legacy lives on,
OL,4,Cone year on from legend's death
OL,6,FJane Bateman and Alex Stepney speak to
OL,7,FVictoria Grimes
OL,9,FSir Bobby Charlton's name is
OL,10,Fcontinuing to make a difference in the
OL,11,Fworld, according to those entrusted to
OL,12,Fcontinue his legacy.
OL,14,FThe England and Manchester United
OL,15,Flegend died on 21 October 2013 at the
OL,16,Fage of 86.
OL,18,FOne of Britain's greatest goal
OL,19,Fscorers, he was a member of the
OL,20,FEngland team that won the 1966 FIFA
OL,21,FWorld Cup.
