OL,3,CSir Bobby Charlton's legacy lives on,
OL,4,Cone year on from legend's death
OL,6,FJane Bateman, vice chair of the Sir
OL,7,FBobby Charlton Foundation, said "Many
OL,8,Fpeople knew of Bobby the great
OL,9,Ffootballer, the gentleman, but not so
OL,10,Fmany people knew there was this
OL,11,Fhumanitarian side to him and that he
OL,12,Feven had a charity.
OL,14,F"So it's been a privilege to be able
OL,15,Fto tell that story about Bobby over
OL,16,Fthe last year."
