OL,3,CSir Bobby Charlton's legacy lives on,
OL,4,Cone year on from legend's death
OL,6,FThe Foundation continues its work with
OL,7,Fa number of initiatives in his name,
OL,8,Fincluding Sir Bobby's Street Reds
OL,9,Fwhich gives footballing opportunities
OL,10,Fto young people in Moss Side,
OL,11,FManchester.
OL,13,FThe charity also sponsors three safe-
OL,14,Fplay hubs near the frontline in
OL,15,FUkraine, and helps provide prosthetic
OL,16,Flimbs for those injured by landmines
OL,17,Fin Cambodia.
