OL,3,CSir Bobby Charlton's legacy lives on,
OL,4,Cone year on from legend's death
OL,6,F"What hurt Bobby the most was when he
OL,7,Fmet children and young people who had
OL,8,Fgone out to play football and come
OL,9,Fback with life-changing injuries.
OL,11,F"He met some of those children and
OL,12,Fyoung people who lost an arm and lost
OL,13,Fa leg. It broke his heart. He couldn't
OL,14,Fturn his back on them. That's where
OL,15,Fthe charity started."
OL,17,FTeammate Alex Stepney was Manchester
OL,18,FUnited's goalkeeper when they became
OL,19,Fthe first English club to win the
OL,20,FEuropean Cup in 1968.
