OL,3,CSir Bobby Charlton's legacy lives on,
OL,4,Cone year on from legend's death
OL,6,FHe helps with the Street Reds scheme
OL,7,Fand said his friend would be pleased
OL,8,Fto know his work continues after his
OL,9,Fdeath.
OL,11,F"Bobby would love it," he said.
OL,13,F"He was a humble guy. When they opened
OL,14,Fthe south stand at Old Trafford and
OL,15,Fcalled it the Sir Bobby Charlton Stand
OL,16,Fhe said to me on the pitch 'I don't
OL,17,Fdeserve this'."
OL,19,FSir Bobby joined Manchester United in
OL,20,F1953, at the age of 16.
